    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Package &amp; install are various phases in maven build lifecycle. package phase will execute all phases prior to that &amp; it will stop with packaging the project as a jar. Similarly install phase will execute all prior phases &amp; finally install the project locally for other dependent projects. </p>\n\n<p>For understanding maven build lifecycle please go through the following link <a href=\"https://ayolajayamaha.blogspot.in/2014/05/difference-between-mvn-clean-install.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://ayolajayamaha.blogspot.in/2014/05/difference-between-mvn-clean-install.html</a></p>\n"
