    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>package</code> will add packaged <code>jar</code> or <code>war</code> to your  <code>target</code> folder, We can check it when, we empty the target folder (using  <code>mvn clean</code>) and then run <code>mvn package</code>.\n<br>\n<code>install</code> will do all the things that <code>package</code> does, additionally it will add packaged <code>jar</code> or <code>war</code> in local repository as well. We can confirm it by checking in your <code>.m2</code> folder.</p>\n"
